bug.short_desc: [regression] all comments are shown as incoming

long_desc.thetext:
As a side-effect of the reverted change for bug 349620 all task comments are shown as incoming. This is due to a different value mapping for task comments:
Mylyn 3.6: comment ID -> comment attribute value Mylyn 3.7 after 1ff7e0bd7ef8653133985473b4eef38a7ae3bbee and before 9f99269112887b9003a6938eb5b59c1eb44f969b comment number -> comment attribute value Mylyn 3.7 after 9f99269112887b9003a6938eb5b59c1eb44f969b: comment ID -> comment attribute value
Additionally Bugzilla changed the attribute value that is used for ID. In Mylyn 3.6 the comment number was set as the attribute value whereas now Bugzilla is using the actual comment ID.
I have pushed a potential fix to this review: http://review.mylyn.org/#change,280
I have pushed the fix to master and kicked off a new build.
